
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-key-l2vpn-vpls-etree-07.txt'>
    <title>"Extension to VPLS for E-Tree", Raymond Key, Simon DeLord, Frederic JOUNAY, Wim Henderickx, Lucy Yong, Lizhong Jin</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-key-l2vpn-vpls-etree-07.txt</link>
    <description>This document proposes a simple and effective approach to emulate E-Tree services over an MPLS network. Section 4 presents a minimal extension to the current VPLS architecture defined in [RFC4761] and [RFC4762] to fulfil the specific E-Tree requirement: Leaf cannot communicate with Leaf. Backward compatibility issues are addressed also.</description>
    <dc:date>2012-04-15T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
